company_benefits_employer_summary:
I'm safe, I belong, I matter.&nbsp;
Part of the journey to make Equinix a place of safety, belonging, and meaning for everyone is our commitment to your wellbeing. Your health and happiness are our highest priority, and we're always working to offer the best benefit options that are comprehensive, innovative and affordable.&nbsp;&nbsp;
Your healthEquinix employees receive excellent health care and counseling plans that vary by country to ensure the well-being of you and your family. We offer paid vacations and holidays and encourage community involvement year-round via volunteer opportunities.
Your familySpending time with your loved ones and taking care of your family are important. Equinix provides a range of country-specific programs that ensure you have the resources needed to thrive and manage your family’s needs.
Your futureEquinix offers different programs to help you build your financial security, make charitable donations and seek additional education. In many countries we also offer a flexible employee stock purchase plan.
There are benefits in place to support you at work, home, and in play.&nbsp;&nbsp;
We have different providers for different benefits, and benefits can be updated or changed at different times of the year. Some benefits can only be updated during the annual open enrollment window, while others can be updated at any time.

